      "raw_text": "Public opinion last night forced\nAhe city council to pass the ordi-\nnance granting to the Spokane &\nPend d'Oreille Rapid Transit COM\npany a franchise over East Pacific\nand East Second avenues. Despite\nthe opposition of the Spokane Trac.\ntion company and the Washington\nWater Power company the ordi-\nnance was passed by a vote of 8\nto 2, Conncilmen Brown and Funk\nbeing the minority."
